course.subject: MATH
course.name: Reading Course: Recent Advances in Generative AI
course.description: This is a reading class to get students familiar with recent advances in generative AI. The course contains three topics: 1) Image generation using diffusion models 2) Large language models; Pretraining and Finetuning; Prompt for LLM; 3) Some advanced topics and multicodal models. Students should seek the course instructor's approval to take this course.
